title: Positive EFT by Silvia Hartmann
description:
New for 2013, Positive EFT is THE ANTIDOTE to depression, anxiety, stress, temper tantrums, low energy, misery, impatience, indecision, confusion and feeling helpless, hopeless, powerless and alone. Positive EFT makes introducing EFT into an easy and thoroughly enjoyable, upliftng experience. It is perfect for self help and an absolute "must have!" resource for the modern practioner. This book is further designed to function as a handouts manual for introduction courses and the full four day Positive EFT training - excellent value for money.
